  "3314790": {
    "name": "四叶草深渊 CLOVERPIT",
    "steam_appid": 3314790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/46c126bc5bcff0ae757d9cbf50faffa0.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" width=780 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/46c126bc5bcff0ae757d9cbf50faffa0.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/46c126bc5bcff0ae757d9cbf50faffa0.mp4?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Clover Pit》是《Balatro》与《Buckshot Roulette》的恶魔结合体，它将玩家困于自我造就的炼狱之中。锈迹斑斑的牢房中仅有一台老虎机和ATM机，你必须在每轮结束时偿清债务，否则将迎来真实的毁灭——绝非虚言！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/8b6c25b4796446818c37aaaf1421e7fb.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/8b6c25b4796446818c37aaaf1421e7fb.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/8b6c25b4796446818c37aaaf1421e7fb.mp4?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控老虎机，赚取额外硬币。借助各类奖励与幸运符触发强力连锁组合，让运势如滚雪球般累积，开启炫目的幸运狂潮！玩弄规则、突破游戏桎梏，在债主步步紧逼下挣扎求生，直至夺取自由！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/d993e46614544908af3d5af0706f8d0a.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/d993e46614544908af3d5af0706f8d0a.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/d993e46614544908af3d5af0706f8d0a.mp4?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/9d249bbcc27933a6af668c22b73e2a72.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/9d249bbcc27933a6af668c22b73e2a72.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>扣人心弦的轻度Rogue体验，每一轮都可能是绝命时刻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/cec578e7e3897751afc1b7b30e6bff30.webp?t=1772010266\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/cec578e7e3897751afc1b7b30e6bff30.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" class=\"bb_img\" width=14 height=14 /></picture></span>跨局成长系统、多结局路线还有各种可解锁的强力道具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/08b01e6eab6d0ad58dc0b6084fa383cc.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" width=14 height=14 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/08b01e6eab6d0ad58dc0b6084fa383cc.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在无尽模式中挑战极限高分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/3f49711e8df2a0b90546a4b11e830900.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" width=14 height=14 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/3f49711e8df2a0b90546a4b11e830900.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>地狱般的密室逃脱氛围！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/d35d5a336ba83642d80c3e7be107eae8.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" width=14 height=14 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/d35d5a336ba83642d80c3e7be107eae8.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>150+种道具与协同效果，助你逆天改命！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/b0f1444f444ecf27b60109ae0c70f4c1.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/b0f1444f444ecf27b60109ae0c70f4c1.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>暗黑成瘾与逃亡交织的残酷物语！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>P.S. 这是赌博游戏吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝对不是！《Clover Pit》是一款轻度Rogue恐怖游戏，绝非老虎机模拟器。游戏中的老虎机生来便是为被玩家破解与征服而设计，绝不索要真实货币！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/2ad6eeb5d3897c51f026b9fcfe150cf9.poster.avif?t=1772010266\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/2ad6eeb5d3897c51f026b9fcfe150cf9.webm?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314790/extras/2ad6eeb5d3897c51f026b9fcfe150cf9.mp4?t=1772010266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
